data.description: Welcome to your Hill Country oasis featuring 2 homes situated perfectly on 5 sprawling acres of picturesque landscape! The main house is a magnificent, custom-built Victorian w/ 5 beds & 3.5 baths. The 1488sqft guest house next door provides additional accommodations, ensuring privacy & comfort. An 800sqft workshop adds a practical touch for those w/ hobbies or storage needs. For outdoor enthusiasts, the full RV hook-up & aquifer well provide convenience & sustainability. As you enter the main house through the grand 2-story entryway, you're greeted by an air of sophistication & charm that sets the tone for the entire residence. The layout is thoughtfully crafted to accommodate various lifestyles for both intimate gatherings & larger social events. The bedrooms are generously proportioned & their spacious design allows for multiple beds. The home has endless possibilities including income-producing potential, a private study or oversized game room. With the potential to customize the outdoor space to suit your desires – whether that's a refreshing pool oasis or additional entertaining area. Beyond the beauty of the estate, the property is a testament to the allure of the Hill Country lifestyle. Strategically located, this estate offers the best of both worlds – the tranquility of country living & the accessibility to urban amenities. Whether you are trying to get to downtown Austin, the Hill Country Galleria offering premier shopping & dining or Mercer Street for its locally-owned favorites like Mazama Coffee & Vintage Soul, they are all just a short drive. Plus, you can be on the lake in a mere 20 minutes & the natural beauty of Hamilton Pool is just a few miles away. Additionally, the renowned wineries of the region are within easy reach. This property is more than a home; it's a canvas for your dreams. Seize the opportunity to make this estate your own and embrace the limitless possibilities it offers for luxurious living in the heart of the Hill Country.
